    },
    {
      "id": "ironmouth_lira_002",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "Patrol passes in forty seconds. You came from the",
        "mine?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ironmouth_lira_003",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "Who are you?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ironmouth_lira_004",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "Someone who's been tracking what the Compact pulled",
        "out of that ruin for three months. My name is Lira. I'm a",
        "Forgewright — or I was, until I read the wrong documents."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ironmouth_lira_005",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "I found references to something called \"Project",
        "Pendulum\" in a classified engineering report. The Compact doesn't",
        "classify engineering reports. That was enough."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ironmouth_lira_006",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "Now. This way."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ironmouth_lira_007",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "She's right. The forest is the only way."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    }
  ]
}
